com.eduworks.foundation.jquery.plugin

Interface Foundation<FullJQuery extends org.stjs.javascript.jquery.JQueryCore<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    FullJQuery - Meaning that the foundation functions can be called on any JQueryCore instances (Including Jquery wrapped elements)

    public interface Foundation<FullJQuery extends org.stjs.javascript.jquery.JQueryCore<?>>
    STJS Wrapper for the foundation functions used in the EC Framework
    Author:
    devlin.junker@eduworks.com
